  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>These apartments are on a self-catering basis so no meals will be provide. Each apartment has a fully equipped kitchen with a ceramic hob, multi-function oven, fridge, dishwasher, coffee-machine, kettle, mixer, steamer and toaster. There are a range of bars and restaurants nearby - perfect for those evenings when you don't feel like cooking.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
