  <description><![CDATA[<p>These luxury apartments have everything you need for your ski holiday. Located in the Obelisque area of <a data-udi="umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606}" title="Montgenevre">Montgenevre,</a> Le Chalets des Dolines represent the charm of traditional alpine villages - warm wooden interiors with views of untouched winter landscapes. As the resort borders Italy, the apartments welcome the sunshine even in the winter. Plus after a day of adventures you can make the most of the wellness area included in your stay.</p>
<h2>Excellent location</h2>
<p>Located at the foot of the pistes, these apartments are right next to the Chalvet slope and Gondola, giving you great access to the slopes and the <a data-udi="umb://document/ac18b1d87c81457eaf0af66a3b8f0b19" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ac18b1d87c81457eaf0af66a3b8f0b19}" title="Milky Way Ski Area">Milky Way ski area</a>. Take advantage of the apartments' ski-in ski-out access and maximise your time exploring fabulous Franco-Italian slopes.</p>
<h2>Spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>These luxury apartments have a high standard of facilities for you to enjoy throughout your stay. The relaxing wellness spa area features an indoor heated swimming pool, whirlpools, saunas, steam room and fitness room . At an additional charge, you can really treat yourself with a full body massage or one of the many facial and beauty treatments on offer.</p>
<h2>Lounge area</h2>
<p>Relax in the comfort of your own private space. Or if you're feeling sociable, there is a cosy s<span>pacious communal lounge area which has a  lovely open fireplace. There's also wine and champagne available to buy and enjoy from reception.</span></p>]]></description>
