  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom apartments</strong> can sleep two to four people and are around 35-40m². These apartments have one twin bedroom and a living area with two pull out beds.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments</strong> can sleep four to six people and are around 45-60m². These apartments have one twin bedroom and one double bedroom, and a living area with two pull out beds. These apartments can be duplex.</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom with cabin apartments</strong> can sleep six to eight people and are around 60-65m². These apartments have one twin bedroom, one double bedroom and a cabin room with bunk beds (suitable for children between 6-14 years old), and a living area with two pull out beds. There is also an additional shower room and toilet in this apartment type.</p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments </strong>can sleep six to eight people and are around 80-95m². These apartments have one double bedroom and two twin bedrooms, and a living area with two pull out beds. There is also an additional shower room and toilet in this apartment type. These apartments can be duplex.</p>
<p>Beds are made on arrival (except sofa beds) and end of stay cleaning is included (except the kitchen and bins, beds must be stripped before departure).</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twin or double beds (please specify when booking)</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Living room</li>
<li>TV with English speaking channels </li>
<li>Telephone </li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Bed linen </li>
<li>Towels </li>
<li>Fully equipped kitchen has four ceramic hobs, multifunction oven, fridge, dishwasher, coffee maker, kettle, blender, steamer, toaster, kitchenware and cleaning kit</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
